                    <span class="post-category"><a href="https://spectator.org/category/politics/">Politics</a></span>                </div>
                <div class="title pf-title">
                    Stephen Moore and Herman Cain Are Just What the Fed Needs                </div>
                                <div class="meta-bar">
                    <div class="author">
                                                <div class="author-text">
                            <span class="italic">by</span> <!-- <span class="uppercase"><a class="pf-author" href="https://spectator.org/author/ralph-benko/">Ralph Benko</a></span> -->
							<span class="uppercase">
							<a href="https://spectator.org/author/ralph-benko/" title="Posts by Ralph Benko" class="author url fn" rel="author">Ralph Benko</a><script>(function() {document.querySelectorAll('.author-text a').forEach((x) => x.className = '')})()</script> 							</span>
